snippet.title: Fates of Ort - trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/895480/Fates_of_Ort/


Fates of Ort is a retro fantasy RPG focused on strategic action, in a land where time is frozen when you stand still. Cast powerful spells - but beware, they will cost you your life. 

Follow development live on Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/topbraj
